    public class RDKitFingerprintNodeModel
extends AbstractRDKitFingerprintNodeModel
    This class implements the node model of the "RDKitFingerprint" node providing calculations based on the open source RDKit library.
    Author:
    Greg Landrum, Manuel Schwarze
